node.text: Did you know we now have a YouTube channel for kids? Tune in to watch @testkitchenkids recipe tester Zoe help her Grandpa Scy learn to make our DIY Edible Spheres! Kids (and their grown-ups!) will love this simple take on a fun molecular gastronomy technique. Turn your favorite liquid ingredients into tasty edible spheres and learn about the science of gelatin. Click the link in our profile to watch now.
